	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non dubito, mi venerande <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>, quin proximas meas literas acceperis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scire autem vehementer aveo, quid istic in suo negocio promoverit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7242" cert="high">Claudius ille Sabaudus</persName> anque illi mutuo dederis aliquantam pecuniam, id quod te per literas ab ipso tibi redditas rogaveram; nam si dedisti, rursus ab hoc <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p506" cert="high">Butlero</persName> nostro, vere angelico <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglo</placeName>, accipies.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is etiam de nostris rebus, quo loco sint, coram reddet certiorem.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commendarem illum tibi, ni scirem iam dudum fuisse ob egregias doteis suas commendatissimum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectamus in horas nunc, quid legati nostri per tabellarium et unum ex famulis, qui equos reducet, scribant.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu, quod facis, scio, domino pro nostrae urbis salute vota facere nunquam cesses, obsecro.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego a proximis literis ne unam quidem literam ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> accepi.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale, cor meum et anima mea, in domino.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">26. Maii 1548.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salveant tui omnes in Christo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Amb[rosius] Bl[aurerus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Man sagt glouplich, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p9708" cert="high">hertzog Ulrich</persName> muͤsß des regiments abtretten, und seyen im ettlich vogteyen ingeben, namlich <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tubingen</placeName>, <placeName ref="l1234" cert="high">Herrenberg</placeName>, <placeName ref="l26" cert="high">Balingen</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1333" cert="high">Duttlingen</placeName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Sonst solle der jung herr an das regiment stohn; der solle ouch dem romischen könig auff bestympt zyl zwaymalhunderttausend gulde erlegen.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">ouch soll die alt fuͤrstin <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l514" cert="high">Urach</placeName> innhaben.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto" ana="salute">Aber ich warten all stund meines lieben schwagers <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8500" cert="high">Peter Schären</persName> des jungen, der euch allweg gantz fruntlich bevilcht von seinen wegen ze gruͤssen; der wirt wol allen bschaid sagen konnen; allsdann schrib ich weyter.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, amico et fratri incomparabili.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
